  "Also note that you don’t pay for model training time, unlike with many typical automated machine learning tools, so feel free to build as many models as you’d like." => "Also note that you don’t pay for model training time, unlike with many typical automated machine learning tools, so feel free to build as many models as you’d like.",
  "A Deep Dive into Data-Driven Campaigns" => "A Deep Dive into Data-Driven Campaigns",
